_sText:
NOTE: I'm aware there are probably a few stairs or rails to choose from here but i spent a bit of time on these so, they are measured well and you can take them apart / adjust length and width easily. Good for someone new to stairs is all.

Extract stairsnrails.vmf to your ' Steam/steamapps/youraccount/sourcesdk_content/cstrike/mapsrc/prefabs ' folder. If you don't have a prefab folder create one. Now you can open the file from the prefabs folder in the same location as all of your maps you've created.

You can use this for anything would be nice to credit me, don't forget to tools/nodraw all of your selections before retexturing!
